Architectural Review Committee
Look over the duties and responsibilities of the Architectural Review Committee, as noted by the Code of Ordinances.
Board of Adjustment
Learn about the Board of Adjustment by reading their sections from the Code of Ordinances.
Commission on Ethics
The Palm Beach County Commission on Ethics strives to promote fairness and integrity in our community.
Finance & Audit Committee
Go over powers and duties of the Finance and Audit Committee.
Infrastructure Surtax Citizen Oversight Committee
The Infrastructure Surtax Citizen Oversight Committee's purpose is to ensure the City's expenditure of surtax proceeds is consistent with Florida Statutes Section 212.055(2).
Local Planning Agency
The Local Planning Agency shall have all of the powers and duties set forth in Florida Statutes Section 163.3161, as amended.
Safe Neighborhood Improvement District
The main objective of the Safe Neighborhood Improvement District is to provide a safe and secure environment for the citizens of the City of Atlantis.
